snippet.textDisplay: Here. Thats it. We have found why Indian Coke Studio and Pakistani Coke studio have such a big disparity. It has nothing to do with the lack of singers in India or the flood of singers in Pak. The Indian coke studio has always been rushing to fuse some indian styles with the west only, while the Pakistani Coke Studio has been fusing its own styles together keeping the essence and the integrity of the rendition in tact. The fusion of a thumri and a qawwali is not only rare, but practically unseen. But fusing them, and bringing in the western flavour is what is the magic of this song. That's how you make art, friends. ❤
snippet.textOriginal: Here. Thats it. We have found why Indian Coke Studio and Pakistani Coke studio have such a big disparity.
